_:N13391c06efd5430c999f3abca0ba8101 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Ian Blakeman joined HM Prison Service (HMPS) in 1986, and was appointed as Director, Commissioning at the National Offender Management Service (NOMS) in October 2013.</p>\n\n<p>His previous roles include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Head of Custodial Commissioning, NOMS</li>\n  <li>Head of Woman and Young People’s Group, HMPS</li>\n  <li>Governor, Leeds Prison</li>\n  <li>Governor, Wetherby Prison</li>\n  <li>Deputy Governor, Wakefield Prison</li>\n</ul>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
